SUMMARY:Coworkers in the Vineyard Lay Ministry Convocation
DTSTAMP:20260413T010450Z
DTSTART:20260423T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Lay ministers in the Archdiocese of Seattle are welcome to join
	 us for the annual Coworkers in the Vineyard Lay Ministry Convocation on T
	hursday\, April 23\, from 9 am to 2:45 pm at Holy Family Parish in Kirklan
	d. Archbishop Etienne will provide guidance for lay ministers\, and Deacon
	 Frank DiGirolamo will give insight into Pope Leo’s Dilexi te. This event 
	is for all professional lay ministers\, and we encourage all laypeople who
	 work for the Church in ministry and parish administration to attend. Lear
	n more and register here: https://archseattle.org/events/lay-ministry-conv
	ocation\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/coworkers-in-the-
	vineyard-lay-ministry-convocation/18291002/2026-04-23T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday 
